// Theme button html
---

<div id="theme_button" class="flex w-fit bg-indigo-400 dark:bg-indigo-500">
  <button
    id="light_theme"
    title="Light theme"
    class="border-2 border-black px-2 pt-1 text-xl hover:cursor-pointer dark:border-indigo-500"
    >🐓</button
  >
  <button
    id="dark_theme"
    title="Dark theme"
    class="border-2 border-indigo-400 px-2 pt-1 text-xl hover:cursor-pointer dark:border-white"
    >🦉</button
  >
</div>
